{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act44side", "eventName": "墟", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AT-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "靈異特輯", "storyInfo": "半夜，疲憊的星熊遇見了怪談中的“輪入道”。追蹤“輪入道”的過程中，她結識了關東煮攤老闆森內。而萌萌香家的電視突然播放起助理澪小姐被人要求謀害自己的畫面，更恐怖的是，沒過多久，澪真的出現在了萌萌香家的門口。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_oldwarehouse_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_catfootstep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？誰在這裡？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monocycle_bell", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車鈴聲？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（揉眼睛）這是夢？我還沒睡醒？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$3", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明亮的月光下，雜物早已被收拾乾淨的地上，分明停著一輛小小的獨輪車。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它就這麼立在地上，沒有依靠任何東西，甚至都沒處在平衡狀態，是往一邊歪著的。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼搞的……我喝多了？才半瓶米酒，怎麼可能？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#10$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更詭異的是，假如真有什麼看不見的東西騎在獨輪車上，那麼，這個東西頭上還戴著一頂比例完全合適的、小小的獨輪車安全帽。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但沒有人知道獨輪車上面到底有沒有“什麼”，所以，在星熊看來，那頂安全帽毫無疑問，正浮在半空中。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警察的竊聽裝置？金兵衛的把戲？鐵齋叔？某種源石技藝？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g5_kajistreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多觀眾都認為青鬼的怪談與輪入道的怪談有關！許多青鬼的受害者都是在目睹輪入道之後遭遇不測，我想——", "name": "輕浮的記者"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_oldwarehouse_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……輪入道？怪談是真的？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之先拿起來看看吧——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monocycle_fast_lp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 1.0, "ystrength": 0.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$3", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "350,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和星熊彎腰同時，獨輪車的踏板飛轉起來，整輛車連同安全帽咻的一聲竄了出去。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等——站住！", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g18_kajistreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 1.0, "ystrength": 0.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monocycle_fast_lp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$3", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨輪車在前面飛馳，星熊跟在後面窮追不捨。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她清清楚楚地看見，踏板帶動車輪，上面的小安全帽有規律地一上一下……"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼看都像是有個看不見的東西在騎車。轉彎時獨輪車的踏板在地上摩擦了一下，甚至還濺起幾星火花。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "xstrength": 1.0, "ystrength": 1.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sit_tatami"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香整個身子一軟，倒在榻榻米上。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……根本睡不著。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然明天早上去一趟事務所吧……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先好好認個錯，態度誠懇一點……實在不行就再多接一點工作，澪小姐會原諒我——", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_largebell", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是鐘聲啊……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#9$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是開著燈和電視睡吧……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香慢慢爬到電視前，按下開關。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吵鬧、誇張、做作，然而就像御機本身一樣令人安心的廣告聲響了起來。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚就先……睡吧。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#4$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……安心與安定的，御機聯合人壽。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（音樂聲）", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位觀眾大家好，歡迎收看金石台的午夜新聞，現在是凌晨一點三十分……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快到丑時三刻了……幽靈最活躍的時間段……嗚……", "name": "萌萌香"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……與北院聯合制定的計劃受阻……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……暴雨襲擊諫崎城，農業地塊受災情況可控……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……接下來讓我們關注受人矚目的御機娛樂產業……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_airdefensealert", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（刺耳的警報聲）", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1", "posfrom": "0,-80", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎、怎麼了？出什麼事了？地震？天災？！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（訊號干擾聲）", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——急通知，緊急通知。這不是演習，這不是演習。", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……目前正遭到北院軍隊的全面攻擊——遭到北院軍隊的全面攻擊——", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了您的人身安全，請遵守以下指示——", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（刺耳的不明聲音）", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "北院軍隊？怎麼可能？！到底發生了什麼事？！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（訊號干擾聲）", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香！萌萌香！萌萌香！", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事，這不是……我的現場直播錄影嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因大家都獨自一人與世浮沉♪", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "些許易逝的溫柔才更讓人不忍♪", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就讓我永遠注視你的——", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（卡頓聲）", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注視你的、注視你的、注視你的、注視你的、注視你的、注視你的——", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——以下指示：請身處室內的居民立刻關閉門窗——", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "電視裡的聲音", "content": "注視你的、"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "電視裡的聲音", "delay": 0.1, "content": "注視你的——"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_container_smash", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香猛地一聲從榻榻米上跳起來。電視裡出現的東西實在過於異常，她把手裡的東西胡亂朝電視丟去。"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊接著，明明沒有轉台，裡面的節目卻又開始換來換去。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……最後的最後，歡迎大家光臨仁田街上的“深夜心動雲獸屋”——", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船~♪信用金庫~♪", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三……三……信……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆……請再給她一次機會。", "name": "熟悉的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個聲音是……？", "name": "萌萌香"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熟悉的女聲從電視裡傳出，萌萌香心中的恐懼慢慢減弱，她把頭從巨大的枕頭後探出一些，嘗試看清螢幕裡的畫面。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,-50"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,-50"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 2.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 6.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.1, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_picturetube", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在是關鍵時刻。", "name": "有點熟悉的男聲"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白。但……我們現在沒有她與鐵齋私下來往的證據。", "name": "非常熟悉的女聲"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "澪小姐？還有集團總裁三船先生？！", "name": "萌萌香"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "電視裡到底在放什麼？錄影？直播？", "name": "萌萌香"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香揉了揉眼睛。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,-50"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,-50"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "澪，她已經不受控了。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕不是受鐵齋指使，這種事有一次就會有第二次。所以，像你之前做的一樣，讓她直接悄無聲息地消失。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船先生，現在這個時間，不適合。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還在幫她求情？", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她現在突然消失，我們勢必要花更多的精力去控制輿論。我怕這會影響到您接下來的計劃。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哼，你說什麼話都是這副表情。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你動了惻隱之心，那好，隨便找個理由，跟她解約，逼她隱退……對了，幫她染上個礦石病。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船先生，這——", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩條路，你自己挑。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了，滿屋的垃圾，她偏偏撿起了那把斷刀，當時我們怎麼找都找不到，只能草草偽造了一把的斷刀。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算她是無心的，事情的性質也已經變了。", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是……", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$p_imp_funnel_end_h", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……礦石病？三船先生……吩咐澪小姐……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓誰得礦石病？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有斷刀……我在滿屋的垃圾裡撿起來的是斷刀？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從“兇宅”的樓上掉下去以後，她草草換了套衣服，把髒衣服包成一團，就離開了節目現場。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那根“棍子”八成是被她順手和髒衣服包在一起了。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香起身走到門口，果然把那根“棍子”從髒衣服中翻了出來。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確是一把斷掉的真刀。"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“事情的性質已經變了”？就因為這把刀？"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她很想立刻把刀丟出窗外，丟得越遠越好，但理智告訴她，這麼做只會惹出更大的麻煩。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是帶著吧。如果、如果有人要的話，我還能還回去，或者，至少……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知是因為從兇宅裡撿了把刀的這個事實，還是因為電視裡三船說話的口氣，一陣惡寒順著她的脊椎一直爬到頭頂。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她把檯燈開了又關，關了又開。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "檯燈亮起，她怕屋外的人看到窗上的剪影。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "檯燈熄滅，她又怕黑暗中突然出現闖入者。"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在商量怎麼處理我嗎？就因為我發了那篇貼文？就因為我撿了把斷刀？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "消失……礦石病？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可能的，一定是搞錯了。他們都沒有提到我的名字——", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodenstairfts", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樓下忽然傳來腳步聲。很熟悉，很穩，很快。"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香已經被各種事逼到了崩潰邊緣。她能猜到來者是誰，但腳步聲每響一次，她就後退一點……"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "350,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一直到退無可退的窗邊。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "duration": 1.0, "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "-150,0"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……萌萌香？", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為你睡了，所以就直接開門進來了。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你之前都會先敲三下門。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們要處置的不是我，對嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "處置？萌萌香，你——", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#10$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直接殺掉，或者染上礦石病……你們說的不是我，對不對？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "澪小姐，剛才不知道為什麼，我的電視突然開始播放……你和三船先生商量要……處理掉某個人的影片。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#21$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#22$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先前只知道我們事務所屬於金石集團，金石集團和金石會有資金上的關係，我以為就只有這種程度，我沒想到……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#22$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你們說的人不是我，對嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香，你先跟我走。這件事還有餘地。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#13$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你們說的……真的是我？！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "64_i16", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g11_odenstall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 5.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我要收拾東西。我要收拾很長很長時間，我要關門了，你在外面等我好嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘴上說著關門，但萌萌香一步也不敢往前走。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而門口的澪也一直站在原地。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會幫你的。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不用，不用你幫，我自己收拾就好。", "name": "萌萌香"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "64_i16", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會幫你的。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "澪小姐，請你不要……", "name": "萌萌香"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "64_i16", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我會幫你的，萌萌香。", "name": "澪"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是面無表情地將一句話重複了三遍，曾經熟悉的身影就在一瞬間變得無比可怕。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾次呼吸過後，就連萌萌香自己也沒有想到，她下一步的動作……"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.5, "yScaleFrom": 1.5, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "yTo": 0.0, "block": "false", "xTo": 0.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是拉開窗戶，從二樓跳了下去。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g11_odenstall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，老闆，剛剛有一輛獨輪車繞過你的攤位過去了，請問你有看到它往哪個方向離開了嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨輪車？哪有什麼獨輪車。", "name": "攤位老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說前面就是仁田街，現在那裡密密麻麻全都是尋歡作樂的人，怎麼可能有人往那邊騎車。", "name": "攤位老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是一般的獨輪車，是一台小的——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小的？多小？", "name": "攤位老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很小，騎得很快，半空中還懸著一頂配套的安全帽。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，這是……昨天晚上那個關東煮攤？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自我介紹一下，我姓森內，森內徹。", "name": "攤位老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定自己在追一輛有安全帽懸在空中的獨輪車？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確定。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那可不是什麼好東西哦。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你追逐的獨輪車，在怪談中被稱為“輪入道”，和“兇宅中的青鬼”差不多是相伴相生的，也有人認為根本就是同一個東西。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對怪談很熟？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是我自誇，這條街上，恐怕沒有人比我更熟悉與怪談相關的事情了。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了找一個……人。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你找的不是什麼二十年前的青鬼。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，怎麼會呢。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要找的，是“神明大人”。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}